(4720, 1, '2017-10-01 12:11:10', '2017-10-01 01:11:10', 'Incomparable to any other residential building in Adelaide, bohem is a statement of architectural ingenuity and stylish indulgence. With a stunning 22-metre vertical garden and plantings that change colour with the seasons, bohem creates a harmonious connection with the serenity of the park square.\r\n\r\nThis exclusive residence offers a 3 bedroom penthouses which will captivate you with unsurpassed sweeping views of Adelaides CBD, stunning coastline or dramatic foothills. The awe-inspiring sense of expanse is enhanced by loft-like, double height ceilings in two of the residences, while each has full length glass sliders forming a seamless transition to the spacious outdoor terraces.\r\nThis bohem penthouse enjoys luxurious indulgence with only the finest of quality and style throughout its interior dcor - the warmth and softness of 100% pure New Zealand wool carpets, the refinement of oak timber parquetry through living and dining room floors, while Miele appliances serve the contemporary and opulent kitchen with its granite island kitchen bench centrepiece.', 'Penthouse at Wrightstreet,Adelaide', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'penthouse-at-wrightstreetadelaide', '', '', '2017-10-01 12:11:10', '2017-10-01 01:11:10', '', 0, 'http://www.smartvilla.com.au/ultimate-auction/penthouse-at-wrightstreetadelaide/', 0, 'ultimate-auction', '', 0),
